The Application is restructured from a single file to files for every method.

1. The __init__ file
The __init__ file is always executed first, according to python compiler.
This file imports all the packages and dependencies that are required by other
files.

2. The routes.py file
This file contains all the route for specific function.

3. The models.py file
This file is connection to database which is then displayed on the frontend.

